<typeStatus id="54C6887B1C53A35AFF23A48FA99F8F8B" box="[151,252,202,228]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BC236D91C53A35AFF05A542AB318ED4" blockId="14.[151,684,262,443]" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">
CONSERVATION STATUS. — With an EO of 
<emphasis id="B909EACB1C53A35AFF23A560A9CB8E51" box="[151,168,293,318]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">c.</emphasis>
<quantity id="4C859B3C1C53A35AFF1BA563A8408E2F" box="[175,291,294,320]" metricMagnitude="7" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9" pageId="14" pageNumber="81" unit="km" value="19000.0">19000 km</quantity>
<superScript id="7C089B911C53A35AFE97A564A84E8E5B" attach="left" box="[291,301,289,308]" fontSize="8" pageId="14" pageNumber="81">2</superScript>
